            <section>
                <title>Competing</title>
                <para>When the character is testing skill versus skill the chatacter makes an
                    Opposing Skill Roll. An opposing skill roll in a roll in which the character
                    attempts to undo an action done previously by another character. Typically the
                    SN of the original action is taken as a negative modifier to the current skill
                    roll.</para>
                <para>Attempting to conceal yourself when others are looking for you is an
                    example.</para>
            </section>
